Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.62,0:00:04.25,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Encounters are mysterious! But cases are even more so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.25,0:00:06.29,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm so glad I'm with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:07.96,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Today is the lemon pie conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:10.03,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Fragrant memories and tender first love!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:11.76,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:13.73,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:16.22,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:39.12,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}We were invited to the birthday party of Asami Uchida,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:42.55,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}rumored to have been Shin'ichi's first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:48.22,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}She fell asleep, so the rest of us went to the Karaoke Room in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.22,0:01:51.82,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That's when one of her friends noticed the lodge was on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:56.36,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Asami Uchida was asleep in the lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:03.33,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Luckily, Ran broke down the door\Nand managed to save her!
